課程教材 Course Material
	    The course materials depend on each research appratus and instructor’s requirement.
Format of Homework
The format of homework assignment depends on each instructor’s requirement.
Format of final project
Students need to choose one of the apparatus introduced in this course to conduct a pilot study. The topic of the project may be corresponding to the student’s thesis or any theme which the student is interested in. Before doing the project, students are encouraged to discuss with one of the instructors of this course about their pilot projects in the process. The format of the final project follows a typical research layout, including introduction, literature review, motivation, specific aim, methodology, results, discussion, and conclusion.    

